Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.06,0:01:55.96,logo,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}{\pos(596,352)}雪酷字幕组
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.97,0:00:32.94,OPJP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I don't wanna let the chance slip away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.97,0:00:32.94,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我不愿让机会溜走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.07,0:00:36.19,OPJP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Why is my freedom taken away?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.07,0:00:36.19,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}为什么要剥夺我的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.35,0:00:38.83,OPJP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Reason is against emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.35,0:00:38.83,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}叛逆情感的缘由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.83,0:00:43.66,OPJP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I've gotta deal with extreme frustration
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.83,0:00:43.66,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是因为我感受到了极大的挫败感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.83,0:00:47.16,OPJP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}All of my efforts will never be in vain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.83,0:00:47.16,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}所有努力将不会是徒劳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.16,0:00:50.23,OPJP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Endless desire,like a haunting refrain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.16,0:00:50.23,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}无尽的欲望难以克制
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.26,0:00:53.54,OPJP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Such a pain,the ideal versus the real
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.26,0:00:53.54,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}理想与现实冲突的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.54,0:00:56.07,OPJP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}There is a way to change the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.54,0:00:56.07,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}有一种方法可以改变世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.10,0:00:57.64,OPJP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Just count on me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.10,0:00:57.64,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}靠我来改变
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.67,0:01:00.94,OPJP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}So what if I sing off-key,who cares
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.67,0:01:00.94,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我歌唱得走调又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.02,0:01:03.02,OPJP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Not good at drawing,no big deal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.02,0:01:03.02,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}画画不行也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.02,0:01:07.78,OPJP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Let me go for my one true belief
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.02,0:01:07.78,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}让我去追寻我的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.86,0:01:09.43,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}克服你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.86,0:01:09.43,OPJP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Overcome yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.62,0:01:12.77,OPJP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}A whole new world god only knows
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.62,0:01:12.77,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一个只有神知道的崭新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:15.67,OPJP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I'll always be on your side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:15.67,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我将永远伴君左右
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.67,0:01:18.87,OPJP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}To be a knight,to be a light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.67,0:01:18.87,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}做你的骑士 做你的明灯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.87,0:01:20.86,OPJP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I'll be shining bright
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.87,0:01:20.86,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}照亮你的前程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.86,0:01:22.58,OPJP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}No more tears everything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.86,0:01:22.58,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}任何情况都不再哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.58,0:01:25.50,OPJP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}That's "God Only Knows"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.58,0:01:25.50,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}那就是所谓的“只有神知道”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:27.57,OPJP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Don't get me wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.57,0:01:29.96,OPJP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}This is the wheel of fate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:27.57,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不要误会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.57,0:01:29.96,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}这是命运的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.96,0:01:32.67,OPJP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I'll do anything for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.96,0:01:32.67,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我会为你做到一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.67,0:01:35.79,OPJP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Whatever happens,my life; turn the page and come of age
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.67,0:01:35.79,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不管人生中发生了什么 只要翻过这一页
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.79,0:01:38.82,OPJP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Every end leads to a new beginning of the next day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.79,0:01:38.82,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}否极终将泰来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.02,0:01:41.62,OPJP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Try to make my life complete,trust myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.02,0:01:41.62,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我会让我的人生完整 请相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:44.25,OPJP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Be strong and do my best
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:44.25,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我会变强 竭尽所能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.28,0:01:48.43,OPJP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Don't look back,carry on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.28,0:01:48.43,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不要回头 继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.43,0:01:51.73,OPJP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love yourself,be happy,it's your life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.43,0:01:51.73,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}要自爱 要开心 这是你的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.73,0:01:57.14,OPJP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Now all we need is to find your life,find your way,for your life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.73,0:01:57.14,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我们所要做的就是为你的人生找到爱与归宿
